يشمل ذلك التكيفات والترجمات أو التنفيذ بأي لغة برمجة أخرى.

Researchers, students, and independent developers may use, analyze, or modify the project for **non-commercial purposes only**.

All such use must include attribution to **RADHWEN DALY HAMDOUNI (رضوان دالي حمدوني)**.

This includes adaptations, translations, or implementation in any other programming language.

